<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>Do not use this class directly. You should use <db:link xlink:href="qt3dcore-qskeletonloader.xml">QSkeletonLoader</db:link> if loading skeleton data from a file (most likely) or <db:link xlink:href="qt3dcore-qskeleton.xml">QSkeleton</db:link> if creating the skeleton and skinned mesh data yourself (mainly for people creating editors or tooling).</db:para>
</db:section>
